  "description": "A wide-angle shot depicts a grey sand beach with several people scattered along the shoreline. The ocean is a mix of turquoise and deep blue, with small waves rolling onto the shore. Several rocky outcroppings are visible in the water, adding depth to the scene. Four people are positioned on the beach; one adult is walking away from the camera, two children are closer to the water's edge, and another child is crouched down, seemingly examining something on the sand. The sky is clear and blue. The lighting suggests a bright, sunny day. The texture of the sand is prominent, and the overall impression is one of a peaceful and natural coastal environment.",
